{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"十三年祭——为鲁迅老人逝世十三周年而作","authors":["徐放"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":20}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"十三年祭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为鲁迅老人逝世十三周年而作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐  放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"近百年来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们用血为人民的祖国打开了路；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十八年来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们跟着毛泽东的大队人马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人民的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已辟出了天下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天高地厚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海阔河深；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗迎风云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城里外的江山好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻过身的劳苦大众，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来的中国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正为着自己的祖国的建设"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修桥补路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开矿建厂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬砖运瓦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好的在耕种庄稼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的祖国是痛苦的，忧愁的；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的祖国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是山青，水秀，人壮，马肥……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经再不是奴隶了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的好老人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有能看到你想望的这崭新的世纪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为这，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为这战斗的胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们愈感到不该丧失了你；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们将永远不会忘记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的号召："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“反对进攻苏联”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也将永远不会违背你的战令："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把标枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向“侵食中国的虎狼”投射出去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你教练我们操习枪法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们被抚育，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们已经变成了人民祖国的坚强武器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的好老人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们发誓："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果敌人敢于侵犯我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不管在任何时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们便将"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英勇地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出击……。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}